commitResults.messageTitle: Update command prefix format to be prefixed by "/"
commitResults.messageBody:
Command prefixes have "/" as their suffixes.

It is more natural to have them prefixed by "/" and this also improves
their scalability.

Let's,
* Update the command prefixes to be prefixed by "/" and followed by
  mandatory whitespace
* Update corresponding tests
Update command prefix format to be prefixed by "/"
